   There have been strange rumblings coming from Volcano Island. Many
adventurers have returned with tales of a mysterious Hall, and a
newly formed cavern. It is said that a great battle is taking place,
but that the help of all races on Darkwind is required to partake
in it.
  The end game of the quest is high level as well, and is a one
on one battle to the death. Getting help on the beginning stages
is allowed, but not with the final battle.
<*><*><*><*><*><*><*><*><*><*><*><*><*><*><*><*><*><*><*><*><*><*><*>
Warning: The plains of the battlefield are an open pk region. PK
players can kill non-pkers, and non-pkers can kill pk'ers. Their
PK status will be unchanged when they leave the battlefield. If
you were non-PK when you entered, you will be non-PK when you exit.
The rewards for the extra challenge might make the risk worthwhile.
